               <p>Q. Can you swear that it was your handkerchief that he gave to the other boy.</p>
               <p>- Newton. Yes, I saw him give it a jurk out of my pocket, I saw his hand employed in taking and discharging of it.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence.</p>
               <p>I was walking up Holborn, he stopped me, and said I had picked his pocket, I never saw him before.</p>
